## Available MCP tools

| Tool | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `mk_list_available_steps` | Next steps to try |
| `mk_add_experiment` | Add an experiment (optional prerequisites) |
| `mk_add_prerequisite` | Break a blocker into prerequisites |
| `mk_mark_completed` | Mark a successful step |
| `mk_mark_failed` | Mark failure and revert |
| `mk_get_graph` | JSON graph + Mermaid |

